label: uncl4453
comment: Code specifying the function of free text.

values.label: Text for subsequent use
values.comment: The occurrence of this text does not affect message processing.

values.label: Text replacing missing code
values.comment: Text description of a coded data item for which there is no currently available code.

values.label: Text for immediate use
values.comment: Text must be read before actioning message.

values.label: No action required
values.comment: Pass text on to later recipient.

values.label: Header
values.comment: Indicates that the text is to be taken as a header.

values.label: Numbered paragraph
values.comment: Indicates that the text starts a new numbered paragraph.

values.label: Paragraph
values.comment: Indicates that the text is a paragraph.
